                <note rend="inline" type="source">800.51 W 89 Lithuania/6: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Commissioner at Riga</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Young</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Riga</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-11-01T17:00:00+01:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 1, 1922—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received November 1—3:35 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>193. Department’s instruction 271, August 8th. Notes to three governments
                    presented today.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Young</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
